firefly
------------------------------------------
Standalone C++ Library for vectors calculations

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.1.7-1
  libfirefly-devel-1.0.0-1bl1
  libfirefly0-1.0.0-1bl1
  libgcc1-10.2.0-1
  libstdc++6-10.2.0-1
  pkg-config-1.6.3-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.34+1git.de9c1b7cfe-1
  cmake-3.17.3-2
  cygport-0.34.0-1
  gcc-core-10.2.0-1
  gcc-g++-10.2.0-1
  ninja-1.10.1-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/tbhaxor/firefly

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/tbhaxor/firefly/archive/1.0.0.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack firefly-1.0.0-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./firefly-1.0.0-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/firefly-1.0.0-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/firefly-1.0.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libfirefly0-1.0.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libfirefly-devel-1.0.0-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(firefly)
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/firefly.README
  /usr/share/doc/firefly/LICENSE
  /usr/share/doc/firefly/README.md

(libfirefly0)
  /usr/bin/cygfirefly-0.dll

(libfirefly-devel)
  /usr/include/firefly.hpp
  /usr/lib/libfirefly.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/firefly.pc

------------------

Port Notes:

